uk.ac.ebi.gxa.utils
Class Deque<T>

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ebi.gxa.utils.Deque<T>

public class Deque<T>
extends Object

A very simple and loose queue implementation based on linked list of arrays (deque). This is basically equivalent to a Deque implementation in Java 6, but means our code retains backwards compatibility with Java 5.
